ygData.messageBody:
Soulfire was RECENTLY found? Hehe someone on Solusek got it about 3 months ago ;) It's a bitch to get it though, the two handed mithril sword comes with less effort, and soulfire is CRAP compared to that..

I am going to guk tonight to try and get ghoulbane, already tried camping it for 7 hours.. I had better luck in lower guk where I got box of abu kar and bag of sewn evil eye in 30 minutes.. And I am only level 28 hehe, but I joined up with a level 45 shaman.. It was a fun ride.. ;)

Now I am gonna take a bath.. bye..

- Avron Akizuki(former Elselynn, now married;)
- Knight of Truth - Solusek Ro
